description:
MindCrack is a server Guude started in late 2010. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

We are approaching the end of Season 3 MindCrack and we are about to reset to a new map when 1.6 comes out. Today we go for a final tour of some of the things I've built on the server.

MindCrack: http://www.youtube.com/user/MindCrackNetwork
